###Get all contacts
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts

###Get a contact by ID. For example:
GET http://localhost:3000/contacts/682650dc0164f4d812e3a49b

###Create a new contact
POST http://localhost:3000/contacts HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Rosemary",
    "lastName": "Smith",
    "email": "roseS19@gmail.com",
    "favoriteColor": "Red",
    "birthday": "23/09/2000"
}

###Update a contact by ID. For example:
PUT http://localhost:3000/contacts/682650dc0164f4d812e3a49b HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Juan",
    "lastName": "Sandoval",
    "email": "Juan284@gmail.com",
    "favoriteColor": "Brown",
    "birthday": "06/10/2000"
}

###Delete a contact by ID. For example:
DELETE http://localhost:3000/contacts/682664aeee13b8b8ebcfbb0c HTTP/1.1
